        "custom_liquid": "<style>.rv{font-family:var(--font-body--family)}.rv__header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem;padding-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.1)}.rv__left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.75rem}.rv__stars-big{color:#FFBE00;font-size:1.5rem;letter-spacing:1px}.rv__count{font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer}.rv__write-btn{padding:9px 18px;border:1.5px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.4);border-radius:6px;font-weight:600;font-size:.875rem;background:transparent;color:var(--color-foreground);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.5rem}.rv__write-btn:hover{border-color:var(--color-foreground)}.rv__grid{columns:4 220px;column-gap:14px}.rv__card{break-inside:avoid;border:1px solid rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.1);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:14px;background:var(--color-background)}.rv__img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4\/3;object-fit:cover;display:block}.rv__body{padding:14px 16px}.rv__name{font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:2px;color:var(--color-foreground)}.rv__date{font-size:.8rem;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.45);margin-bottom:6px}.rv__stars{color:#FFBE00;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:1px}.rv__text{font-size:.875rem;line-height:1.65;color:rgba(var(--color-foreground-rgb),.75)}@media(max-width:749px){.rv__grid{columns:2 160px}}<\/style>{%- assign imgs = product.images -%}<div class=\"rv\"><div class=\"rv__header\"><div class=\"rv__left\"><span class=\"rv__stars-big\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/span><span class=\"rv__count\">20 Reviews &#9660;<\/span><\/div><button class=\"rv__write-btn\">Write a review &#x2261;<\/button><\/div><div class=\"rv__grid\"><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 0 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[0] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Ally J.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">2\/18\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Just had a kid, and this is 1000% THE way to lose the baby weight. And at your pace, too. \uD83D\uDC9C<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 1 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[1] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Ruth B.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">2\/23\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">As someone who has an office job and sorely misses the life of constant walking that I had in retail, this is just perfection. \u2728 I use it daily.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 2 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[2] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Marg<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">2\/20\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">This machine is the reason I haven\u2019t missed a workout day in 3 months. I\u2019m not even joking.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 3 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[3] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Ashley F.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">2\/23\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">So good!<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Mitzi N.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/24\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Love it! Barely takes any effort to get started and the rocking motion feels so natural on my joints. I do 30 minutes while watching TV.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 0 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[0] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Sarah K.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/1\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">I\u2019ve tried so many fitness gadgets and this is the only one I\u2019ve actually stuck with. 3 months in and still going strong!<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Jennifer M.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">2\/28\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Great low-impact workout. My knees thank me every single day. Wish I\u2019d found this sooner.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\">{%- if imgs.size > 1 -%}<img class=\"rv__img\" src=\"{{ imgs[1] | image_url: width: 400 }}\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">{%- endif -%}<div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Tom R.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/10\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Really solid build quality. I use it while watching TV and barely notice the time passing. Good investment.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">Lisa C.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/15\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Lost 8 pounds in the first month just using this for 20 minutes a day. My energy levels are through the roof. Amazing!<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"rv__card\"><div class=\"rv__body\"><div class=\"rv__name\">David W.<\/div><div class=\"rv__date\">3\/20\/2026<\/div><div class=\"rv__stars\">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;<\/div><p class=\"rv__text\">Bought this for my wife and she loves it. Now I use it too. Best purchase we\u2019ve made this year. Highly recommend!<\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>",
